thread.title: Maureen Baulden

author: Guest
title: Maureen Baulden
text:
Graveside services for Mrs. Maureen Ann Baulden, 77, of Killeen will be held Tuesday at 10 a.m. at the Garden of Memories Cemetery in Killeen.
Mrs. Baulden died Feb. 8, 2024, in Temple. She was born June 15, 1946, in New Orleans, Louisiana.
